1. give the name to the screen
# screen -S patching

2. List screen
# screen -ls
# screen -list

3. Shortcut to open a new screen within screen
ctrl+ac

4. How to Rename a Screen Window
ctrl-a+shift-A

5. Switching Between Screen Terminal Windows, List screen windows
ctrl-a+shit-"

6. shortcut to detach from screen
ctrl-ad

7. how to reattach to screen when it is already attached
screen -rd 1284.patching

8. check the version of screen
# screen --version

9. Kill screen session
ctrl-a+k

10. Move to next screen windows
ctrl-a+n or ctrl-an

11. Move between current and previous window
ctrl-aa

12. How to jump to particular screen window
ctrl-a+2
